platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Un classique à ne pas manquer
華麗過招重現武術之美

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We love BioWare for Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic and their other epic role-playing games, but this particular gem from their back catalog shines like a glorious green dragon. Infused with Chinese myth and populated by unforgettable characters, Jade Empire: Special Edition is a beautiful update of the classic action-RPG. The intuitive touch controls make it that much easier for us to get lost in its massive, martial-arts world of intrigue, adventure—and even a bit of romance.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Try this remastered classic from the makers of Mass Effect.
La version remasterisée du grand classique.
